    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable daily driver. Mechanically, the car is sound; the engine starts easily and it handles well on the road. However, there are visible signs of wear and tear, including several scratches and minor dings on the exterior body panels. Inside, the upholstery shows some fading and minor stains consistent with regular use. It has been well-serviced, but it is not a showroom piece. If you need a reliable car and don't mind some cosmetic imperfections, this is a great value.",
