    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and mechanical integrity. This selection offers a refined driving experience, featuring a preserved interior and a documented service history. It represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of performance and long-term value. Fully inspected to ensure it meets our professional standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic presentation.",
