    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking for a new home for this absolute gem of a car! It\u2019s been super reliable and is in wonderful shape, perfect for someone who wants a solid, high-quality ride without the 'brand new' price tag. It drives like a dream and has been really well-loved and taken care of. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
